And we found out, that all this is still easy… compared to doing it during or right after fighting with a swerve strong defense…</p>","post_number":14,"post_type":1,"posts_count":20,"updated_at":"2022-04-13T19:49:31.463Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":13,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":5,"reads":444,"readers_count":443,"score":208.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":405472,"topic_slug":"advice-on-shooting-while-moving","display_username":"Giora Kornblau ","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"","reply_to_user":{"id":1267,"username":"Jared_Russell","name":"Jared Russell","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/jared_russell/{size}/399_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":6}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":28070,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":"Lead mentor"},"post_url":"/t/advice-on-shooting-while-moving/405472/14","custom_user_title":"Lead mentor","reactions":[{"id":"heart","type":"emoji","count":6}],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":6,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3043321,"name":"Susan Clay","username":"susanclay","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/46a35a/{size}.png","created_at":"2022-04-13T19:58:25.727Z","cooked":"<p>I think I took a similar approach to what <a class="mention" href="/u/jacob6838">@jacob6838</a> was suggesting and canceled out the robot’s velocity instead of trying to account for the ball’s velocity as I described in my initial post.<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/original/3X/f/3/f3a9cd0e4603b47a94ab90347bbbabc397085330.jpeg" data-download-href="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/f3a9cd0e4603b47a94ab90347bbbabc397085330" title="20220413_125125"><img src="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f3a9cd0e4603b47a94ab90347bbbabc397085330_2_375x500.jpeg" alt="20220413_125125" data-base62-sha1="yLxOYQLC4qzLSKNJh97a9fiTs88" width="375" height="500" srcset="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f3a9cd0e4603b47a94ab90347bbbabc397085330_2_375x500.jpeg, https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f3a9cd0e4603b47a94ab90347bbbabc397085330_2_562x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/f/3/f3a9cd0e4603b47a94ab90347bbbabc397085330_2_750x1000.jpeg 2x" data-dominant-color="BCB4A4"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename">20220413_125125</span><span class="informations">3024×4032 364 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>
